{"data":[{"id":564185613,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564185613","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546339534,"updated_time":1546339534,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":14,"comment_count":13,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我真的很难过。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e翻了一圈回答，都在说营销，吹牛，知乎要完。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e讥讽他四两拨千斤轻松骗关注，嘲笑他读书太少想的太多浅薄愚蠢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但换个角度来看这件事呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个高中生，已经开始学习高于高中数学的知识，开始试着探索数学世界的难题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当他因为局限性，觉得自己证明成功了。他带着欣喜，带着少年心气地发到知乎上来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e从头到尾，他也只不过犯了每一个少年人都犯过的错误，他只是把世界想的简单，把自己想的复杂。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个孩子初来到世界，开始学着走路，突然觉得自己能去跑马拉松，就算天真，又为什么要嘲笑他？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可世界就是这么可悲，当前辈对后辈不是鼓励，不是引导，而是讥讽嘲笑，又谈什么少年强则中国强？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在他已经销了知乎账号，但我相信他依然翻看你们的回答。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个十几岁的男孩，该如何承受这些恶意和嘲弄？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他可能以后再也不敢碰数学书，不敢提哥德巴赫猜想，不敢去相信自己有数学天赋。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们因为自己的优越感，毒杀了一个少年。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我真的很难过。翻了一圈回答，都在说营销，吹牛，知乎要完。讥讽他四两拨千斤轻松骗关注，嘲笑他读书太少想的太多浅薄愚蠢。但换个角度来看这件事呢？ 一个高中生，已经开始学习高于高中数学的知识，开始试着探索数学世界的难题。当他因为局限性，觉得自己…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=105\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelation